## Instructions
1. Identify papers this work `builds_upon` (key prior work that this paper extends).
2. Identify papers this work `contradicts` (findings or claims that are challenged).
3. Identify papers this work `replicates` (reproduced experiments).
4. Identify papers whose datasets are reused (`uses_dataset_from`).
5. Identify papers whose methods are reused (`uses_method_from`).
6. Use paper titles or arXiv IDs as identifiers. Return [] if not applicable.

## Output Format
